# All Star Cleaning тАФ Project Context

Marketing website for an Ottawa exterior cleaning service. Goal: convert visitors to phone calls. 1000+ static pages (900 programmatic: 45 locations ├Ч 5 services ├Ч 2 locales ├Ч 2 route patterns).

**Stack**: Astro 6.3 + React 19, Cloudflare Pages (`output: 'static'`), Tailwind CSS v4, Keystatic CMS (JSON in `src/content/`).

## Critical Conventions

1. **Path alias**: `@/*` тЖТ `src/*`. Never use `../` chains.
2. **Prop name**: Layout `schema` prop (singular) тАФ never `schemas`.
3. **JSON-LD**: Use generators from `src/seo/` тАФ never hand-write structured data.
4. **Tailwind tokens**: Use CSS vars from `src/styles/global.css @theme`. Never hardcode hex. Never reference `--tw-*` (renamed to `--c-*` in prod by obfuscation plugin).
5. **Static only**: No backend, no DB. Forms via Web3Forms. No server-side code.
6. **No tests/lint**: Only `npm run typecheck` (astro check) available.

## Routes

```
/[locale]/                                      тЖТ Homepage
/[locale]/services/[serviceSlug]                тЖТ 5 service pages
/[locale]/area/[locationSlug]/[serviceSlug]     тЖТ 450 programmatic (location-first, canonical)
/[locale]/services/[serviceSlug]/[locationSlug] тЖТ 450 programmatic (service-first, mirrors above)
/[locale]/area/ | /about | /reviews | /contact | /privacy | /terms | /sitemap
/keystatic/* | /api/keystatic/*                 тЖТ CMS, exempt from i18n middleware
```

## Layouts

Always use one of these тАФ never inject `<head>` or JSON-LD manually:

- **`PageLayout.astro`**: Use for all content pages. Props: `title`, `description`, `locale`, `schema`, `breadcrumbs`, `heroTitle`, `heroSubtitle`.
- **`BaseLayout.astro`**: Lower-level wrapper (head + header + footer). `PageLayout` uses this internally.

## Adding Content

- **New location**: Append to `src/data/locations.ts` тАФ 900 programmatic pages auto-generate.
- **New service**: Create `src/content/services/{slug}.json`, add import + array entry in `src/data/services.ts`.

## Build Obfuscation

Production build renames `--tw-*` тЖТ `--c-*`, Tailwind layer names тЖТ generic names, `/_astro/` тЖТ `/static/`. HTML comments are stripped. No source maps. Do not reference internal Tailwind vars.

## AI Traps тАФ Do Not Break These

| Trap | Rule |
|------|------|
| **Domain** | Always `https://allstarcleaning.ca` тАФ no `www.`. Two hardcoded places: `astro.config.mjs` `site:` + `BaseLayout.astro` `siteUrl`. Must match. |
| **`neighbours`** | Values in `src/data/locations.ts` `neighbours` arrays are EN slug strings, not `Location` objects. |
| **URL slugs** | Both `/en/` and `/fr/` routes use English `slug`, never `frSlug`. |
| **`as unknown as Service`** | Intentional double cast in `services.ts`. Keystatic JSON тЙа strict TS interface. Do not remove. |
| **Root redirect** | `src/pages/index.astro` тЖТ `/en/` always. No Accept-Language detection. |
| **`_routes.json` тЖФ middleware** | Both must list the same Keystatic bypass paths. |
| **`schema` prop** | Layouts take `schema` (singular). `schemas` is silently ignored. |
